+# P3.3 Hardening: replay, SQL fallback, quarantine
+
+1. Use `scripts/check_execution_replay_consistency.py --quarantine-on-critical` during incident review.
+2. If `trade_execution_replay_sql_fallback_total` spikes, inspect `orders:exec` retention and checkpoint freshness.
+3. If `execution_replay_mismatch_total{severity="critical"}` fires, keep degraded mode enabled and review quarantined `sid` before unquarantine.
+4. `trade-execution-rebuild-state.timer` can safely rebuild `orders:state:*` because `orders:exec` remains SoT.
